Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Grattan Business Park is a prime mixed use Business Park ideally located within close proximity to the entrance of Clonshaugh Business and Technology Park. it offers occupiers an excellent location just 6 km north of Dublin’s City Centre and 2 km south of Dublin Airport with excellent access to the M50, M1 and Dublin Port Tunnel.

Clonshaugh Business and Technology Park is an established business campus and home to very many well-known companies such as Amazon, Allergan, 3 Mobile, Vodafone, BT Ireland, Butlers Chocolates and Magnet Networks.


Key Features

-Energy efficient LED Panels lighting

-Electric heating

-Perimeter trunking

-Automated roller shutter door to each unit

-Sealed concrete floor

-Clear internal height of approx. 6.6 metres to warehouse

-3 phase power

-High speed internet connection available

-High quality 2 storey offices with suspended ceiling size approx. 131-137 sqm.

-Flexible Size Options

-Ample parking

-Sizes ranging from 301-308 sqm




Call us today to arrange a viewing.
